reviewText: I chose this rating because I was fortunate to have some workshops with Delihah.  I already had the VHS version, but wanted the DVD version.

The moves are covered well enough for those with the basics of belly dance already downpat. If you are pondering this for a first purchase, Neena and Veena or Atea would be your best options. If you have already had a few beginner classes this DVD will be perfect for you. It contains a wealth of information.
